OL,6,F"We go around and we run dementia
OL,7,Fawareness sessions, workshops and we
OL,8,Ftell people what dementia is, how to
OL,9,Fidentify the symptoms and how they can
OL,10,Fsupport and manage the person that's
OL,11,Fgot dementia.
OL,13,F"We need to bring dementia out into
OL,14,Fthe open just like we brought cancer
OL,15,Fout into the open."
OL,17,FNearly a million people in the UK are
OL,18,Fcurrently living with dementia and the
OL,19,Fnumbers are rising.
