OL,6,FAccording to Alzheimer's Research UK,
OL,7,Fit's estimated that one in two people
OL,8,Fwill be affected by the condition
OL,9,Feither through having it or caring for
OL,10,Fa loved one.
OL,12,FHe said: "I want to create an
OL,13,Fenvironment, Bristol city if you like,
OL,14,Fwhere people with dementia can go into
OL,15,Fa shop, or they can go into a school,
OL,16,For they can go into a club and they
OL,17,Fcan be accepted for who they are.
OL,18,FThat's what I want."
