OL,6,FTony cared for his wife Barbara for
OL,7,Fmore than 20 years as she struggled
OL,8,Fwith dementia.
OL,10,FThe first signs came with simple
OL,11,Fepisodes of forgetfulness, but as the
OL,12,Fcondition progressed, Barbara had to
OL,13,Fgive up her job as a nursery nurse.
OL,15,F"One thing we decided right at the
OL,16,Fbeginning, is we'll fight this every
OL,17,Finch of the path. We'd fight it all
OL,18,Fthe way and we did."
