OL,3,CPeople with dementia 'treated like
OL,4,Csecond-class citizens'
OL,6,F"She became mute, she became a
OL,7,Fwheelchair user, she stopped eating or
OL,8,Fcertainly had problems eating and so I
OL,9,Fused to make her food so that she
OL,10,Fcould easily digest it."
OL,12,FBarbara passed away in 2022, but Tony
OL,13,Fwants to use her legacy to drive his
OL,14,Fwork to help others.
